    "U.S.C. Title 7 - AGRICULTURE 7 U.S.C. United States Code, 2024 Edition "
    "Title 7 - AGRICULTURE CHAPTER 106 - COMMODITY PROGRAMS SUBCHAPTER I - "
    "DIRECT PAYMENTS AND COUNTER-CYCLICAL PAYMENTS Sec. 7913 - Availability of "
